Job description 1 : 
Meeting with the design team to discuss the needs of the company
Building and configuring Magento 2 eCommerce websites
Coding of the Magento 2 templates
Developing Magento 2 modules in PHP using best practices
Setting performance tasks and goals
Troubleshooting various integration issues.
Updating website features and security patches
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Job description 2 : 
Proficient in OOP and its application
Good understanding of Design Patterns used in Magento Open Source/Adobe Commerce
