Job description 3 : 
At least 3+ years of front-end Magento development experience.
Proficiency in client-side technologies including HTML and CSS.
Complete understanding of responsive web design and related development techniques.
Understanding of MVC architecture patterns.
Excellent knowledge on Magento theme and customizing on it for complex front-end development.
Good knowledge on Magento existing functionality and multi website concept.
